UserPKG
=======
![alt logo](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dracolinux/UserPKG/master/res/hicolor/48x48/UserPKG.png)

Unprivileged package manager for Linux/BSD.

UserPKG is a convenient front-end for pkgsrc, simplifiying the installation and usage of third-party software. No administrator access needed.

Requirements
============

* Linux/BSD
* Build essentials

Status
======

Early Alpha, but usable.

Roadmap/TODO
============

